#     enabled (alongside BUGSEE_SIZE_ANALYSIS_ENABLED), the agent
#     queries the appserver for the most recent prior build's
#     recorded artefact size and compares it to the current build.
#     Crossing a configured threshold prints `warning:` / `error:`
#     prefixed lines and (on FAIL) exits non-zero. Each threshold
#     below is independently optional; a value of 0 / unset disables
#     that gate. Negative deltas (artefact shrunk) never trigger.
#
