#   BUGSEE_SIZE_CHECK_FAIL_PCT          e.g. 10.0 → fail at +10%
#   BUGSEE_SIZE_CHECK_WARNING_BYTES     e.g. 500000 → warn at +500 KB
#   BUGSEE_SIZE_CHECK_FAIL_BYTES        e.g. 2000000 → fail at +2 MB
#
